{"tid":2196743,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"音樂高材生仙女氣質好戀愛　笑容甜到蛀牙啦！","createTime":"2020-09-10T06:24:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-10T06:47:52.000Z","uid":217211,"like":3,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8c2acdda1064d75a755a448b567dc7a1525c93c4","tid":2196743,"uid":217211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T06:24:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.mymypic.net/data/attachment/forum/202008/26/113045cfw449mfnmmmjjri.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mymypic.net%2Fdata%2Fattachment%2Fforum%2F202008%2F26%2F113045cfw449mfnmmmjjri.jpg&h=0cb272dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n來自中國江蘇的音樂高材生Julie ジュリ，畢業於伯克利音樂學院及慶應義塾大學研究所，有著被音樂長期陶冶下自然散發出的仙女氣質，外貌也是TOP等級，笑起來更是甜到讓人蛀牙，內涵和外表兼具，根本就是極品天菜！<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.mymypic.net/data/attachment/forum/202008/26/112950zrs1s8rsrb2zf2i2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mymypic.net%2Fdata%2Fattachment%2Fforum%2F202008%2F26%2F112950zrs1s8rsrb2zf2i2.jpg&h=e98f3015&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://www.mymypic.net/data/attachment/forum/202008/26/112950d4j46cdlcasj2ldm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mymypic.net%2Fdata%2Fattachment%2Fforum%2F202008%2F26%2F112950d4j46cdlcasj2ldm.jpg&h=5aac25c2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://www.mymypic.net/data/attachment/forum/202008/26/112950s077rks7l7mbkmm1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mymypic.net%2Fdata%2Fattachment%2Fforum%2F202008%2F26%2F112950s077rks7l7mbkmm1.jpg&h=5e7c3ae2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nJulie ジュリ大學就讀的美國伯克利音樂學院，是全世界規模最大且最頂尖的獨立現代音樂學院，她畢業後又繼續在日本的名門大學慶應義塾大學繼續就讀研究所，曾參加過選秀節目《創造101中國版》，現在開始在日本藝能界發展，雖然還沒闖出名氣，但她的顏值絕對不輸線上那些火紅的女藝人。<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.mymypic.net/data/attachment/forum/202008/26/1129518okmkkcmr1r18g1a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mymypic.net%2Fdata%2Fattachment%2Fforum%2F202008%2F26%2F1129518okmkkcmr1r18g1a.jpg&h=410ca4c0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://www.mymypic.net/data/attachment/forum/202008/26/112951dandunmd5md53xx4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mymypic.net%2Fdata%2Fattachment%2Fforum%2F202008%2F26%2F112951dandunmd5md53xx4.jpg&h=d5750c1b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://www.mymypic.net/data/attachment/forum/202008/26/112949yuuonkio55zuo5bn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mymypic.net%2Fdata%2Fattachment%2Fforum%2F202008%2F26%2F112949yuuonkio55zuo5bn.jpg&h=109f1456&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nJulie ジュリ的Instagram內滿滿的美照，還有玩抖音、彈鋼琴、唱歌的影片，雖然外表氣質，感覺有點距離感，但其實Julie ジュリ是個活潑的女孩，個性也是非常可愛呢！<img src=\"https://www.mymypic.net/data/attachment/forum/202008/26/112950xsbyukgn1bkxxnrz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mymypic.net%2Fdata%2Fattachment%2Fforum%2F202008%2F26%2F112950xsbyukgn1bkxxnrz.jpg&h=b22dad28&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://www.mymypic.net/data/attachment/forum/202008/26/112951k44uku8kbduuku6u.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mymypic.net%2Fdata%2Fattachment%2Fforum%2F202008%2F26%2F112951k44uku8kbduuku6u.jpg&h=32178a85&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://www.mymypic.net/data/attachment/forum/202008/26/112952b7f05pjj490j49r0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mymypic.net%2Fdata%2Fattachment%2Fforum%2F202008%2F26%2F112952b7f05pjj490j49r0.jpg&h=fcf9df87&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"536e31882c49794099612ae265ededd9845f4ecc","tid":2196743,"uid":217211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T06:24:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6a63880bdef2940970f619e1d67dc81a7940f50","tid":2196743,"uid":37146,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T06:28:20.000Z","msg":"正係正<br />\n但好